Akash Palkhiwala -- Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer

Yeah. Mike, from a QTL perspective, really legal costs have been at a stable lower level for the last several quarters. And so the margin profile that you're seeing kind of reflects stabilization of the legal cost. And really, it's about the top-line revenue and focusing on kind of expanding and keeping the licensing business steady going forward.

Operator

