Huawei represent or represented 16% of the market. That becomes available to us across all of our OEMs. So that's driving a situation that demand is outpacing supply. We're happy what we see right now on the premium tier.

For example, in high tier, we see share gains in fiscal '21, and we expect the situation to normalize toward the second half of the year.

