Akash Palkhiwala -- Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer

Yeah. So a couple of factors, Stacy, it's Akash. First is, as I indicated in my prepared remarks, we typically see a kind of a resetting of certain expenses on the opex side. So you have opex growth that happens between the December and the March quarter.

